article_title: Putin Freezes Vodka Prices to Calm Protestors
article_text:
SIGN UP FOR OUR NEWSLETTER

Russian president Vladimir Putin ordered a freeze on vodka prices after a 30 percent increase since 2013.

SIGN UP FOR OUR NEWSLETTER

Euronews reported, “The announcement to cap vodka prices coincides with the release of a survey showing the mood for protest in thew country was growing.”
